properties.areaDesc: Waters from Cascade Head to Florence OR from 10 to 60 nm; Coastal waters from Cascade Head to Florence OR out 10 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued March 2 at 2:13PM PST until March 4 at 3:00AM PST by NWS Portland OR
properties.description:
* WHAT...Seas greater than 9 ft expected.


- Seas: Seas will gradually build to 9 to 11 ft late tonight
before peaking in the 11 to 13 ft range on Tuesday.


* WHERE...Coastal waters from Cascade Head to Florence OR out 10
NM and Waters from Cascade Head to Florence OR from 10 to 60
NM.

* WHEN...From 6 AM Tuesday to 3 AM PST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM TUESDAY TO 3 AM PST WEDNESDAY
